Packages to install:

gnuradio-companion
gnuradio-dev
libxml2
libxml2-dev
bison
flex
cmake
git
libaio-dev
libboost-all-dev
swig

sudo apt install gnuradio-dev libxml2 libxml2-dev bison flex cmake git libaio-dev libboost-all-dev swig

The following GITHUB repos are also needed:

git clone https://github.com/analogdevicesinc/libiio.git
cd libiio
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr .
make 
sudo make install
cd ..

git clone https://github.com/analogdevicesinc/libad9361-iio.git
cd libiio
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr .
make 
sudo make install
cd ..

git clone https://github.com/analogdevicesinc/gr-iio.git
cd libiio
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr .
make 
sudo make install
cd ..
